# ICM Repo-as-a-Workspace — required environment variable NAMES.
#
# Names only — never commit values. Values are stored in GitHub Secrets and
# injected into the container at runtime by GitHub Actions. See SPEC.md Part 5.
#
# The dispatch workflow generates its `env:` block from this file.

# --- Base set (required by every workspace) ---
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
GITHUB_TOKEN=

# --- Workspace-specific variables ---
# Add additional variable names below as workspaces require them.
